{
  "name": "RPlog_Looking_For_Old_Soldiers",
  "title": "Looking for Old Soldiers",
  "summary": "The amnesiac Serenella and her Twi'lek companion Ka'una set out to dig into Serenella's hidden past, beginning with a frank conversation in their hotel room about who she once was. Dressed for the part, they share a meal at an upscale restaurant where they reconnect with the charming Jalek Wessiri, trading flirtatious banter and probing for leads. Their search takes them to the small Freedom Fighters of Efavan Museum, where the curator Maxxen pulls old enlistment records and photographs from his archives. A snapshot captioned 'Naughty Kitty' and a name, Aerith Fenn, briefly raise Serenella's hopes before proving dead ends, though the trail eventually points toward a Marine named Rhade Terrel. Grateful for Maxxen's patient help, the pair leave a quiet donation and depart with a copy of the photo, one small step closer to the truth.",
